                        <h3>Customer Segmentation</h3>
                        <p>This notebook performs exploratory data analysis on a dataset of customer demographics, purchase history, and online behavior. It utilizes Python and Pandas to analyze metrics like average transaction amount, purchase frequency, and customer age distribution. The analysis aims to uncover insights to guide customer segmentation for targeted marketing. </p>
